239
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,120
Saya menginginkan kartu Permaisuri.

240
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:01,930
Ayo.

241
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,120
Jangan lari.

242
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,560
Mereka bersama kita.

243
00:15:17,010 --> 00:15:25,620
