Ayo pergi!

268
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,440
Katakan padaku sekarang!

269
00:17:30,510 --> 00:17:33,160
Tuan, Marquis Wu'an mengatakan bahwa
beliau sedang sibuk dengan urusan militer.

270
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:33,920
